<li id="cite_note-9"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-9">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFOstling1999" class="citation book cs1">Ostling, Richard and Joan (1999-10-20). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://archive.org/details/mormonamericapow00ostl/page/60"><i>Mormon America</i></a>. HarperCollins. pp.&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://archive.org/details/mormonamericapow00ostl/page/60">60–63</a>. <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-0-06-066371-1" title="Special:BookSources/978-0-06-066371-1"><bdi>978-0-06-066371-1</bdi></a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Mormon+America&amp;rft.pages=60-63&amp;rft.pub=HarperCollins&amp;rft.date=1999-10-20&amp;rft.isbn=978-0-06-066371-1&amp;rft.aulast=Ostling&amp;rft.aufirst=Richard+and+Joan&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Farchive.org%2Fdetails%2Fmormonamericapow00ostl%2Fpage%2F60&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ACriticism+of+the+Church+of+Jesus+Christ+of+Latter-day+Saints" class="Z3988"></span></span>
