<li id="cite_note-Compton_1997-10"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Compton_1997_10-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Compton_1997_10-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="#CITEREFCompton1997">Compton 1997</a></span>
