<li id="cite_note-Ostling78-52"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Ostling78_52-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Ostling78_52-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFOstling1999" class="citation book cs1">Ostling, Richard and Joan (1999-10-20). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://archive.org/details/mormonamericapow00ostl/page/78"><i>Mormon America</i></a>. HarperCollins. pp.&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://archive.org/details/mormonamericapow00ostl/page/78">78–79</a>. <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0-06-066371-5" title="Special:BookSources/0-06-066371-5"><bdi>0-06-066371-5</bdi></a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Mormon+America&amp;rft.pages=78-79&amp;rft.pub=HarperCollins&amp;rft.date=1999-10-20&amp;rft.isbn=0-06-066371-5&amp;rft.aulast=Ostling&amp;rft.aufirst=Richard+and+Joan&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Farchive.org%2Fdetails%2Fmormonamericapow00ostl%2Fpage%2F78&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ACriticism+of+the+Church+of+Jesus+Christ+of+Latter-day+Saints" class="Z3988"></span></span>
