<li id="cite_note-176"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-176">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFSmith,_Joseph1840" class="citation book cs1"><a href="/wiki/Joseph_Smith" title="Joseph Smith">Smith, Joseph</a> (1840). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://archive.org/details/bookmormon01smitgoog"><i>Book of Mormon</i></a> (3rd revised&#160;ed.). Nauvoo, Illinois: Robinson and Smith. p.&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://archive.org/details/bookmormon01smitgoog/page/n119">115</a>. <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/1-60135-713-3" title="Special:BookSources/1-60135-713-3"><bdi>1-60135-713-3</bdi></a><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">2009-08-03</span></span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Book+of+Mormon&amp;rft.place=Nauvoo%2C+Illinois&amp;rft.pages=115&amp;rft.edition=3rd+revised&amp;rft.pub=Robinson+and+Smith&amp;rft.date=1840&amp;rft.isbn=1-60135-713-3&amp;rft.au=Smith%2C+Joseph&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Farchive.org%2Fdetails%2Fbookmormon01smitgoog&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ACriticism+of+the+Church+of+Jesus+Christ+of+Latter-day+Saints" class="Z3988"></span></span>
