<li id="cite_note-177"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-177">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">The wording "white and a delightsome" was introduced in the 1st edition of the Book of Mormon in 1830. This was changed to "pure and a delightsome" in the 3rd edition in 1840. The 1841 and 1849 European editions of the Book of Mormon were printed in England by the Twelve Apostles, and were the <a href="/wiki/Kirtland,_Ohio" title="Kirtland, Ohio">Kirtland</a> 2nd edition with <a href="/wiki/American_and_British_English_spelling_differences" title="American and British English spelling differences">Anglicized spellings</a>. Future LDS editions were based on the European editions until the church issued a major reworking in 1981. <link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFCrawley,_Peter1997" class="citation book cs1">Crawley, Peter (1997). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20110611230856/http://contentdm.lib.byu.edu/u?%2Frsc%2C3772"><i>A Descriptive Bibliography of the Mormon Church, Volume One 1830–1847</i></a>. Provo, Utah: <a href="/wiki/Religious_Studies_Center" title="Religious Studies Center">Religious Studies Center</a>, <a href="/wiki/Brigham_Young_University" title="Brigham Young University">Brigham Young University</a>. p.&#160;151. <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/1-57008-395-9" title="Special:BookSources/1-57008-395-9"><bdi>1-57008-395-9</bdi></a>. Archived from <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://contentdm.lib.byu.edu/u?/rsc,3772">the original</a> on 2011-06-11<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">2009-02-12</span></span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=A+Descriptive+Bibliography+of+the+Mormon+Church%2C+Volume+One+1830%E2%80%931847&amp;rft.place=Provo%2C+Utah&amp;rft.pages=151&amp;rft.pub=Religious+Studies+Center%2C+Brigham+Young+University&amp;rft.date=1997&amp;rft.isbn=1-57008-395-9&amp;rft.au=Crawley%2C+Peter&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fcontentdm.lib.byu.edu%2Fu%3F%2Frsc%2C3772&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ACriticism+of+the+Church+of+Jesus+Christ+of+Latter-day+Saints" class="Z3988"></span></span>
</li>
