<li id="cite_note-217"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-217">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFGreene2016" class="citation news cs1">Greene, David (7 July 2016). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.npr.org/2016/07/07/485058737/mama-dragons-try-to-prevent-suicides-among-mormon-lgbt-children">"Mama Dragons Try To Prevent Suicides Among Mormon-LGBT Children"</a>. <a href="/wiki/NPR" title="NPR">NPR</a><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">29 November</span> 2016</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Mama+Dragons+Try+To+Prevent+Suicides+Among+Mormon-LGBT+Children&amp;rft.date=2016-07-07&amp;rft.aulast=Greene&amp;rft.aufirst=David&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2F2016%2F07%2F07%2F485058737%2Fmama-dragons-try-to-prevent-suicides-among-mormon-lgbt-children&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ACriticism+of+the+Church+of+Jesus+Christ+of+Latter-day+Saints" class="Z3988"></span></span>
